      <title>美国国税局认为它可以对抗特朗普的诉讼，但无论如何还是达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/admin/irs-trump-lawsuit-deal.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们写了一份备忘录，概述了质疑特朗普总统对国税局提起的诉讼的方法。相反，政府正在设立一个补偿基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/admin/irs-trump-lawsuit-deal.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 19:25:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国税局禁止对特朗普及其家人进行审计</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/trump-irs-doj-lawsuit-audit.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为司法部赔偿基金协议的一部分，官员们发誓不会追究任何悬而未决的事项，包括涉及特朗普总统纳税申报表的事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/trump-irs-doj-lawsuit-audit.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 19:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
